                <ITEXT FONT="NewAster Roman" FONTSIZE="5" FCOLOR="Black" FSHADE="80" CH=" melee attacks are allowed."/>
                <para ALIGN="0" LINESPMode="0" LINESP="5.5"/>
                <ITEXT FONT="NewAster Roman" FONTSIZE="5" FCOLOR="Black" FSHADE="80" CH="† A same-level or lower attacker more than their own height away can only target your torso (half-exposed, −2 to hit); groin, legs, and feet are unreachable. Head down also removes neck, eyes, and face from reachable targets."/>
